name: Shot on iPhone - Macro Edition
description:
My first NFT on HEN collection!

This photo is my first ever macro photo shot on iPhone 5 with using Olloclip 4-in-1 lens in May 2015.

When I was at high school, photography has been started to be a passion for me. I went to Trabzon for an travel project. After we had our lunch, I saw that daisy in front of the restaurant and I took the photo. Thanks for reading my story :)

I will give an airdrop for the collectors of my NFTs. 


2448x3264 px | 300 dpi | 3.1 MB
